I'd reduce the power of Bonus Domain by breaking it into two feats
(non-epic).

Extra Domain Spellcasting
You gain access to spells from another domain.
Prereq: domain spellcaster
Benefit: Choose another domain you have access to.  You can prepare
and cast spells from this domain as from your other domains.
Special: You may take this feat more than once, choosing a different
domain each time.

Extra Domain Power
You gain another domain power from another domain.
Prereq: domain spellcaster, Extra Domain Spellcasting
Benefit: Choose a domain for which you have taken Extra Domain
Spellcasting.  You can use the domain power of this domain.
Special: You may take this feat more than once, choosing a different
domain each time.

The domain spells share the domain slot at each spell level.

Keith
